label: Discuss with husband/partner if/when would like to get pregnant again
codebookDescription: 71b. Discuss if and when Id like to get pregnant again with my husband/partner  Jadili kuhusu iwapo na lini ningependa kuwa mjamzito tena na mme/mwenzio

label: Discuss specific family planning methods with husband/partner
codebookDescription: 71c. Discuss specific family planning methods with my husband/partner.  Jadili kuhusu mbinu mahususi za upangaji uzazi na mume/mwenzio.

label: Fully express my opinions about family size and family planning methods with husband/partner
codebookDescription: 71d. Fully express my opinions about family size and family planning methods with my husband/partner  Toa maoni yangu kuhusu ukubwa wa familia na mbinu za upangaji uzazi na mume/mwenzio

label: Ask husband/partner to use a condom if I want him to
codebookDescription: 71e. Ask my husband/partner to use a condom if I want him to  Kumuuliza mume/mwenza wangu kutumia mpira iwapo ninataka atumie

label: Reach an agreement with my husband/partner about use of family planning
codebookDescription: 71f. Reach an agreement with my husband/partner about use of family planning that takes my desires into account  Fikia maamuzi  na mume/mwenzaio kuhusu mbinu ya upangaji uzazi ambayo inachukulia mapendeleo yangu maanani

label: Choose a family size, time between births, or family planning method that mother in law does not agree with
codebookDescription: 71g. Choose a family size  time between births  or family planning method that my mother in law does not agree with  Chagua ukubwa wa familia  muda kati ya kuzaa  au mbinu ya upangaji uzazi ambayo mama mkwe hakubaliani nayo

label: Start a family planning method if friends and family might find out

label: Continue a family planning method if friends and family found out
codebookDescription: 71i. Continue a family planning method if my friends and family found out  Endelea na mbinu ya upangaji uzazi iwapo familia na marafiki watafahamu

label: Bring up the topic of family planning with a health care provider
codebookDescription: 71j. Bring up the topic of family planning with a health care provider  Tambulisha mada ya upangaji uzazi na mhudumu wa Afya

label: Ask a provider questions I have about family planning methods
codebookDescription: 71k. Ask a provider questions I have about family planning methods  Muulize mhudumu maswali ninayo kuhusu  mbinu za upangaji uzazi

label: Ask a provider if I'm not sure something I've heard about family planning is true or not
codebookDescription: 71l. Ask a provider if Im not sure something Ive heard about family planning is true or not  such as a potential side effect I have heard from other women  Muulize mhudumu iwapo sina uhakika na ukweli wa jambo fulani kuhusu upangaji uzazi ambalo nimesikia

label: Ask a provider to clarify something they have told me about family planning
codebookDescription: 71m. Ask a provider to clarify something they have told me about family planning if Im not sure I understand  Muulize mhudumu kufafanua jambo ambalo wameniambia kuhusu upangaji uzazi na ambalo sina uhakika iwapo nimeelewa

label: Tell a provider what is important to me in choosing a family planning method
codebookDescription: 71n. Tell a provider whats important to me in choosing a family planning method  Mwambie mhudumu ni nini kilicho cha maana kwangu katika kuchagua mbinu ya upangaji uzazi

label: Have some control over if and when I get pregnant again
codebookDescription: 71o. Have some control over if and when I get pregnant again  Ithibithi iwapo na nitakapopata ujauzito

label: Choose a family planning method that will work well for me
codebookDescription: 71p. Choose a family planning method that will work well for me  Chagua mbinu ya upangaji uzazi ambayo itakuwa bora kwangu

label: Obtain the method of family planning I want, if I want one
codebookDescription: 71q. Obtain the method of family planning I want  if I want one  Pata mbinu ya upangaji uzazi ambayo ninayotaka na iwapo nitataka

label: Obtain a different method of family planning if the one I want is not available
codebookDescription: 71r. Obtain a different method of family planning if the one I want isnt available  Pata mbinu tofauti ya upangaji uzazi iwapo na ambayo ninaitaka haipatikani

label: Find solutions to bothersome side effects from family planning or switch methods if needed
codebookDescription: 71s. Find solutions to bothersome side effects from family planning or switch methods if needed because of bothersome side effects  Pata suluhu kwa athari zitokanazo na kutumia njia fulani ya upangaji uzazi au badilisha mbinu iwapo nitahitajika kwa sababu

label: Use a family planning method according to instructions to prevent pregnancy
codebookDescription: 71t. Use a family planning method according to instructions to prevent pregnancy  Tumia mbinu ya upangaji uzazi kutegemea maelekezo ili kuzuia kupata ujauzito

label: Stop using family planning and get pregnant again if and when I want to
